{"id":"lyr_5p2O5YWL5Yuk_MzIwMA_0010","text":"天高海闊珍惜不夠","structure":{"line_index":10,"char_count":8},"semantics":{"themes":["珍惜","失去","自然"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["天高海闊","珍惜","不夠"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,3,9,4,3,3,3,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["tin1","gou1","hoi2","fut3","zan1","sik1","bat1","gau3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"天高海闊","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"珍惜","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"不夠","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"感嘆廣闊的天地自然，人們卻不懂得珍惜，直到失去才後悔，語氣帶有惋惜。"},"source":{"title":"花落誰家","artists":["李克勤"],"lyricists":["林若寧"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_3200","prev_line_id":"lyr_5p2O5YWL5Yuk_MzIwMA_0009","next_line_id":"lyr_5p2O5YWL5Yuk_MzIwMA_0011","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
