{"id":"lyr_5p2O5YWL5Yuk_MzIwMA_0017","text":"這個八月天氣很冷 再見快樂炎夏","structure":{"line_index":17,"char_count":14},"semantics":{"themes":["氣候異常","告別","快樂"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["八月","冷","炎夏"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,4,4,2,3,4,9,5,4,4,4,2,0,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ze5","go3","baat3","jyut6","tin1","hei3","han2","laang5","zoi3","gin3","faai3","lok6","jim4","haa6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"這個","pos":"DET"},{"text":"八月","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"天氣","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"很","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"冷","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"再見","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"快樂","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"炎夏","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"描寫反常的氣候（八月寒冷），並以此告別快樂的夏天，象徵美好時光的逝去，語氣顯得傷感。"},"source":{"title":"花落誰家","artists":["李克勤"],"lyricists":["林若寧"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_3200","prev_line_id":"lyr_5p2O5YWL5Yuk_MzIwMA_0016","next_line_id":"lyr_5p2O5YWL5Yuk_MzIwMA_0018","paragraph_id":"para_04"}}
