{"id":"lyr_5p2O5YWL5Yuk_MzIwMA_0026","text":"儘管擁有 怕一切變得罕有","structure":{"line_index":26,"char_count":11},"semantics":{"themes":["擁有","失去","恐懼"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["擁有","罕有","怕"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[9,9,9,5,4,3,4,4,3,9,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["zeon2","gun2","jung2","jau5","paa3","jat1","cai3","bin3","dak1","hon2","jau5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"儘管","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"擁有","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"怕","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"一切","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"變得","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"罕有","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"即使擁有，也害怕一切變得稀少罕有，表達了對失去的恐懼，語氣顯得不安。"},"source":{"title":"花落誰家","artists":["李克勤"],"lyricists":["林若寧"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_3200","prev_line_id":"lyr_5p2O5YWL5Yuk_MzIwMA_0025","next_line_id":"lyr_5p2O5YWL5Yuk_MzIwMA_0027","paragraph_id":"para_05"}}
